WEBVTT

00:00:01.247 --> 00:00:05.126
After days of negotiation,
for the very first time,

00:00:05.168 --> 00:00:08.087
my parents allowed me
to step out unescorted

00:00:08.129 --> 00:00:10.131
for a movie with my friends.

00:00:10.173 --> 00:00:13.384
I was 14 and beyond excited

00:00:13.426 --> 00:00:16.262
with this new freedom I had.

00:00:16.304 --> 00:00:19.807
With a big smile on my face,
I ended up at the back of the theater.

00:00:20.850 --> 00:00:23.519
And just ten steps from my seat,

00:00:23.519 --> 00:00:27.148
I felt these heavy hands
grab both my breasts.

00:00:27.148 --> 00:00:29.817
And before I knew it,
these hands disappeared.